Chemicals

Company Overview of Ecovative Design LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Ecovative Design LLC is a biomaterials company that envisions, develops, produces, and markets earth friendly sustainable materials. Its products include Myco board that is used for furniture components and work surfaces; Myco foam that is used in packaging, insulation, and acoustics development applications; Myco make for use in teddy bears, balls, and more; and Myco flex and grow materials. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Green Island, New York.


70 Cohoes AvenueGreen Island, NY 12183United StatesFounded in 2007



Phone: 518-273-3753

