Ecovative Design LLC Key Developments

Ecovative Design Gets $9.1 Million DARPA Contract for Living Materials
Jun 29 17
Ecovative Design said that it has been awarded a $9.1 million defense contract. The contract with the Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency, or DARPA, is to develop living building materials. An idea being explored would be to literally grow shelters or other structures in places where they are needed.


